---

<Layout title="MMC Astro UI 组件展示中心" description="全面展示 MMC Astro 网站的所有 UI 组件，包括手风琴、文章卡片、商业表单、搜索功能、轮播组件、团队卡片和视频卡片等。">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-accent/5 to-background">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
            MMC Astro UI 组件展示中心
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-text-default mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            全面展示 MMC Astro 网站的所有 UI 组件，这些组件都基于现代设计理念，
            采用 MMC 品牌风格，为用户提供优秀的交互体验。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <span class="bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">UI组件</span>
            <span class="bg-accent text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">设计系统</span>
            <span class="bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">用户体验</span>
            <span class="bg-accent text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">前端开发</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

      <!-- Stats Showcase Section -->
      <section class="py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
          <SectionTitle
            sectionTitle="统计展示组件"
            description="展示公司核心成就和关键数据的统计卡片组件"
          />
          <StatsShowcase />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Button Components Section -->
      <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
          <SectionTitle
            sectionTitle="按钮组件"
            description="多种样式的按钮组件，支持不同尺寸和变体"
          />
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">主要按钮</h3>
              <Button variant="primary" size="sm">小按钮</Button>
              <Button variant="primary" size="md">中等按钮</Button>
              <Button variant="primary" size="lg">大按钮</Button>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">轮廓按钮</h3>
              <Button variant="outline" size="sm">小按钮</Button>
              <Button variant="outline" size="md">中等按钮</Button>
              <Button variant="outline" size="lg">大按钮</Button>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">透明按钮</h3>
              <Button variant="outline-transparent" size="sm">小按钮</Button>
              <Button variant="outline-transparent" size="md">中等按钮</Button>
              <Button variant="outline-transparent" size="lg">大按钮</Button>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">链接按钮</h3>
              <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" size="sm">联系我们</Button>
              <Button href="/services" variant="outline" size="md">查看服务</Button>
              <Button href="/about" variant="secondary" size="lg">关于我们</Button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Customer Logos Section -->
      <section class="py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
          <SectionTitle
            sectionTitle="客户标志展示"
            description="展示合作客户标志的跑马灯组件"
          />
          <CustomerLogos />
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Marquee Component Section -->
      <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
          <SectionTitle
            sectionTitle="跑马灯组件"
            description="可自定义的跑马灯滚动组件"
          />
          <div class="relative flex items-center overflow-hidden before:absolute before:top-0 before:left-0 before:z-10 before:h-full before:w-20 before:bg-gradient-to-r before:from-gray-50 before:to-transparent after:absolute after:top-0 after:right-0 after:h-full after:w-20 after:bg-gradient-to-l after:from-gray-50 after:to-transparent">
            <Marquee 
              items={[
                { name: "示例1", logo: "/images/customers/company-logo/rakan jaya.webp", alt: "示例1" },
                { name: "示例2", logo: "/images/customers/company-logo/salamku.webp", alt: "示例2" },
                { name: "示例3", logo: "/images/customers/company-logo/Teck Guan.webp", alt: "示例3" },
                { name: "示例4", logo: "/images/customers/company-logo/anniks.webp", alt: "示例4" },
                { name: "示例5", logo: "/images/customers/company-logo/LWL.webp", alt: "示例5" }
              ]}
              duration="15s"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Call to Action Section -->
      <section class="py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
          <SectionTitle
            sectionTitle="行动号召组件"
            description="用于引导用户采取行动的营销组件"
          />
          <CallToAction />
        </div>
      </section>

    <!-- Search Form Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="搜索功能演示" 
          description="体验我们的搜索表单组件，支持内容搜索功能"
        />
        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
          <SearchForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Accordion Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="服务流程展示" 
          description="手风琴组件用于展示步骤流程，支持展开/收起交互"
        />
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <Accordion />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Cards Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="文章卡片展示" 
          description="文章卡片组件用于内容中心展示文章，支持多种内容类型和标签"
        />
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          {sampleArticles.map((article) => (
            <ArticleCard article={article} />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Cards Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="团队成员展示" 
          description="团队卡片组件用于展示团队成员信息，包括头像、职位和描述"
        />
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          {sampleTeamMembers.map((member) => (
            <TeamCard {...member} />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Video Cards Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="视频内容展示" 
          description="视频卡片组件用于展示视频内容，支持 YouTube 视频和视频信息"
        />
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          {sampleVideos.map((video) => (
            <VideoCard {...video} />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Swiper Slider Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="客户见证轮播" 
          description="轮播组件用于展示客户见证，支持自动播放和响应式设计"
        />
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <SwiperSlider />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Business Form Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <SectionTitle 
          sectionTitle="商业合作表单" 
          description="专业的商业合作申请表单，支持多种合作类型和完整的项目信息收集"
        />
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <BusinessForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Summary Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-accent/5 to-background">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">组件使用总结</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-default mb-8">
            以上展示的所有 UI 组件都遵循了 MMC 的设计规范，具有统一的设计语言和优秀的用户体验。
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary/20 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">🎨 设计特点</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-default text-left">
                <li>• 统一的品牌色彩方案</li>
                <li>• 现代化的圆角设计</li>
                <li>• 优雅的阴影效果</li>
                <li>• 响应式布局支持</li>
                <li>• 流畅的动画过渡</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent/20 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">⚡ 功能特点</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-default text-left">
                <li>• 完整的交互功能</li>
                <li>• 无障碍访问支持</li>
                <li>• 移动端优化</li>
                <li>• 易于定制和扩展</li>
                <li>• 性能优化</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary/20 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">📊 组件统计</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-default text-left">
                <li>• 基础组件: 5个</li>
                <li>• 表单组件: 3个</li>
                <li>• 展示组件: 8个</li>
                <li>• 交互组件: 3个</li>
                <li>• 营销组件: 2个</li>
                <li>• 总计: 21个UI组件</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border border-primary/20 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">🚀 开始使用</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-text-default mb-6">
              这些组件已经集成到 MMC Astro 的设计系统中，您可以在任何页面中轻松使用它们。
              每个组件都经过精心设计，确保与整体网站风格保持一致。
            </p>
            <p class="text-text-default">
              如需了解更多技术细节或自定义选项，请参考 
              <code class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm">UI_COMPONENTS_GUIDE.md</code> 文档。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
